OL,6,FIn 2022, the Guardian reported that,
OL,7,Faccording to a leaked copy of the
OL,8,Fdocument, the report concluded the
OL,9,Forigins of the "deep-rooted racism of
OL,10,Fthe Windrush scandal" lie in the fact
OL,11,Fthat from 1950 to 1981 "every single
OL,12,Fpiece of immigration or citizenship
OL,13,Flegislation was designed at least in
OL,14,Fpart to reduce the number of people
OL,15,Fwith black or brown skin who were
OL,16,Fpermitted to live and work in the UK".
