OL,4,Cto reveal roots of scandal
OL,6,FParty leader Sir Keir Starmer said in
OL,7,FJune that if elected he would ensure
OL,8,F"urgent reform" of the compensation
OL,9,Fscheme to make it more efficient, a
OL,10,Frestoration of the Windrush Unit to
OL,11,Fthe Home Office, and a Windrush
OL,12,Fcommissioner "to be the voice of
OL,13,Ffamilies affected".
OL,15,FAhead of the expected publication of
OL,16,Fthe report, Windrush campaigner
OL,17,FPatrick Vernon said the significance
OL,18,Flay in a commitment to transparency
OL,19,Faround government and policy-making.
