OL,6,FHe said: "I think what's important now
OL,7,Fwith the new Government and Keir
OL,8,FStarmer making his speech yesterday at
OL,9,Fthe Labour conference, he talked about
OL,10,Fa duty of candour for Hillsborough,
OL,11,Ffor the Post Office, and also made
OL,12,Freference to Windrush.
OL,14,F"And this report - even though really
OL,15,FI don't think it'll make that much
OL,16,Fdifference to be quite honest in terms
OL,17,Fof the ongoing battle for the needs of
OL,18,Fthe Windrush victims - it reinforces
OL,19,Ftransparency around government."
