OL,4,Cto reveal roots of scandal
OL,6,FMany lost homes and jobs and were
OL,7,Fdenied access to healthcare and
OL,8,Fbenefits. When the scandal was
OL,9,Funcovered, the Conservative government
OL,10,Fpromised to right the wrongs of what
OL,11,Fhad happened but the compensation
OL,12,Fscheme has been repeatedly criticised
OL,13,Ffor the speed at which claims are
OL,14,Fbeing processed and payments made.
OL,16,FMr Vernon said: "We're still waiting
OL,17,Fto have more details from the (new
OL,18,FLabour) Government about how they're
OL,19,Fgoing to tackle and resolve the
OL,20,FWindrush scandal, in particular the
OL,21,Fcompensation scheme."
